  <h2>Why we exist</h2>
  <p>
    Modern social apps are loud, lonely, and full of strangers performing for strangers.
    Duncit flips the script. We help you discover people who actually match your vibe — locally,
    instantly, and without the pressure of dating apps or the noise of mega platforms.
  </p>

  <h2>What we believe</h2>
  <ul>
    <li><strong>Real over polished.</strong> Authenticity beats algorithms.</li>
    <li><strong>Energy over ego.</strong> The right vibe matters more than the right filter.</li>
    <li><strong>Safety first.</strong> Always, no exceptions.</li>
    <li><strong>Joy is the metric.</strong> If you didn't smile today, we failed.</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>Where we're going</h2>
  <p>
    Duncit launches in 2026 with mobile-first apps for iOS and Android. We're starting small — a
    handful of cities — and scaling with the community, not at it. Want in early?
    <a href="/">Join the waitlist</a>.
  </p>

  <h2>The team</h2>
  <p>
    A tiny crew of designers, engineers, and community builders spread across three continents,
    united by one belief: friendship is a feature worth fighting for.
  </p>
